text: The Unknown Mariachi () is a 1953 Mexican comedy movie directed by Gilberto Martínez Solares and starring Germán Valdés, Rosa de Castilla, Gloria Mange, Rosita Fornés, Marcelo Chávez, Tito Novaro, Lupe Carriles. ==Other websites== * Category:1953 comedy movies Category:Mexican comedy movies Category:Movies directed by Gilberto Martínez Solares
title: The Unknown Mariachi
